    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "robe worn by military officials with a round collar, unstitched open sides, and no wrapped fabric along the bottom",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "博物館で、平安時代の武官が着ていた脇明けの装束が展示されていた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-pro"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "時代祭の行列で、脇明けを身につけた武官の役を見ることができる。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-pro"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "この絵巻物には、脇明けを着て馬に乗る武士の姿が描かれている。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-pro"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": [
            {
              "text": "わきあけも、襟も、乱るる姿は、電燭の霜に、冬牡丹の葉ながらくずるるようであった。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "怨霊借用",
                "author": "泉鏡花",
                "note": "青空文庫"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "まさはよっぽどくたびれたと見え、絣の羽織のわきあけから懐手をしたまま、首をたれ黙って合点をしている。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "鏡餅",
                "author": "宮本百合子",
                "note": "青空文庫"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2,
        "gloss": "small opening in the side of traditional Japanese clothing (where the sleeve meets the bodice, below the armpit)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
